# List of _Beyblade Burst Evolution_ episodes

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Jump to: navigation, search

_**Beyblade Burst Evolution**_ is the 2017 sequel to the [anime](/wiki/Anime
"Anime") television series _[Beyblade Burst](/wiki/Beyblade_Burst "Beyblade
Burst")_. It was adapted by [OLM](/wiki/OLM,_Inc. "OLM, Inc.") and aired in
all [TXN](/wiki/TX_Network "TX Network") stations in Japan on April 3,
2017.[1] The opening theme is "EVOLUTION BURST!". From episodes 1-26 the first
ending theme is "Beyxercise". From episodes 27 onwards the second ending theme
is "Beyxercise 2".

##

_" Sekai e! Varukirī Shinka!!"_ (世界へ!ヴァルキリー進化!!) | April 3, 2017 | November 4, 2017 (Canada)

against one another, friendship quickly fades.

December 16, 2017 (United States)  
The current captain of the AS Gallus, Daigo, is an old pal of Valt and
